com.skratchdot.electribe.model.esx

Interface SampleInPatternInfo

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SampleInPatternInfoImpl

    public interface SampleInPatternInfo
    A representation of the model object 'Sample In Pattern Info'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Index
    • Pattern Label
    • Part Count
    • Part List

    See Also:
    EsxPackage.getSampleInPatternInfo()
